{"title_page": "Indiana", "text_new": "{{About |the U.S. state of Indiana}}did you know you can eat your faces burgers and poo. you can also pee on your toilet without poking in the poo face. you can also eat your city\n{{Redirect|Hoosier State|the passenger train|Hoosier State (train)}}\n{{pp-pc1|small=yes}}\n{{use American English|date=August 2019}}\n{{short description|State of the eastern central United States}}\n{{Use mdy dates|date=December 2019}}\n{{Coord|40|N|86|W|display=title|region:US-IN_type:adm1st_scale:3000000}}\n{{Infobox U.S. state\n| name = Indiana\n| official_name = State of Indiana\n|ElectoralVotes = 11<ref>{{cite web|title=Electoral College Information|url=http://www.in.gov/sos/elections/2979.htm|website=in.gov|accessdate=January 12, 2016}}</ref>\n| image_flag = Flag of Indiana.svg\n| flag_link = Flag of Indiana\n| anthem = [[On the Banks of the Wabash, Far Away]]\n| image_seal = Indiana-StateSeal.svg\n| image_map = Indiana in United States.svg\n| nickname = The [[Hoosier]] State\n|Former = Indiana Territory\n| population_demonym = [[Hoosier]]\n| motto = [[The Crossroads of America]]\n| seat = [[Indianapolis]]\n|LargestCity = capital\n|LargestMetro = [[Indianapolis metropolitan area|Greater Indianapolis]]\n|Governor = {{nowrap|[[Eric Holcomb]] ([[Republican Party (United States)|R]])}}\n|Lieutenant Governor = {{nowrap|[[Suzanne Crouch]] (R)}}\n|Legislature = [[Indiana General Assembly|General Assembly]]\n|Upperhouse = [[Indiana Senate]]\n|Lowerhouse = [[Indiana House of Representatives]]\n|Senators = {{nowrap|[[Todd Young]] (R)}}<br />{{nowrap|[[Mike Braun]] (R)}}\n|Representative = 7 Republicans<br />2 Democrats\n| postal_code = IN\n|TradAbbreviation = Ind.\n|OfficialLang = [[English language|English]]\n| area_rank = 38th\n| area_total_sq_mi = 36,418\n| area_total_km2 = 94,321\n| area_land_sq_mi = 35,868\n| area_land_km2 = 92,897\n| area_water_sq_mi = 550\n| area_water_km2 = 1,424\n| area_water_percent = 1.5\n| population_as_of = 2019\n| populat